1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvali Isus i Marija, kako ste mi?

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ste svi dobro?

3
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Niste?

4
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pokušajte se sjetiti što večeras tražite ovdje.

5
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ste večeras ovdje?

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam sinoć u Splitu i onda mi jedna gospodža postavi pitanje u dvorani nakon predavanja:

7
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je tako teško doći do Boga?

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto se tako lako spustiti nizbrdo u zlo?

9
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je teško razgovarati s Isusom?

10
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odgovorio sam joj: "Gospođo, vi ste pobrkali neke stvari."

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Teško je biti dobar čovjek i teško je biti pošten čovjek i teško se truditi da drugoga voliš.

12
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] I teško je biti strpljiv.

13
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali doći do Isusa to je najlakše u životu.

14
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad si najgori, najgrešniji, Isus je tu i stoji pred tvojim ratima.

15
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad si ti rastrešen, on je tu i gledate i pitate: "Zar nećeš sa mnom razgovarati?"

16
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa opće nije teško pronaći.

17
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, ljudi ga traže na krivim putevima.

18
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je problem?

19
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako hoćeš nekoga vidjeti, onda nećeš ušima osluškivati, je li on tu?

20
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako hoćeš nekoga slušati, kako govorim, da nećeš očima slušati glazbu i gledati u CD kako svira.

21
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako hoćeš naći Boga, onda ga nećeš naći tako kako razgovaraš s ljudima.

22
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nećeš ga naći u nekakvim meditacijama, kako to obično ljudi misle, pa ni u trasedentalojni yogi, a kamoli u drugima.

23
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Boga se nalazi tamo gdje On jest.

24
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ideš po Zagrebu i hoćeš pod svaku cijeru naći klokana, nećeš ga naći, osim ako postoje u Zološkom vrtu.

25
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tražiš na krivom mjestu krive stvari.

26
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:27,060
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ako hoćeš pronaći Boga, onda ti nema drugog izlaza, nego moraš ići tamo gdje se On nalazi.

27
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] A gdje se On nalazi?

28
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:33,560
[SPEAKER_00] Nalazi se samo u tom odgovoru na pitanje, a tko sam zapravo ja?

29
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:36,919
[SPEAKER_00] I odakle ja dolazim na svijet? I zašto ja moram živjeti?

30
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:40,319
[SPEAKER_00] I tko je to ovaj svijet? Zašto Zagreb uopće postoji?

31
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] I čim si postaviš pitanje, šta je to ovo razapeto nebo iznad nas?

32
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dokle to dopire?

33
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:55,800
[SPEAKER_00] I ako se samo upitaš, a gdje je ova naša zemlja u svemiru?

34
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] Je li zemlja na kraju svemira, usred svemira, na rubu?

35
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:06,719
[SPEAKER_00] Mi uopće ne znamo gdje je zemlja u svemiru, jer ne poznamo ni svemir.

36
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] I čim počneš se pitati, a čija sam ja?

37
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto ja moram živjeti?

38
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto ja moram umrijeti?

39
00:03:18,599 --> 00:03:20,379
[SPEAKER_00] A što je to smrt?

40
00:03:20,379 --> 00:03:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kamo sad to ide sa smrću?

41
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:25,300
[SPEAKER_00] A gdje su mene moji roditelji uzeli?

42
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje su me našli?

43
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:28,879
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto moja majka nije mene mogla htjeti?

44
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:32,219
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto uopće ne znam odakle sam ja došla na svijet i došao na svijet?

45
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:36,080
[SPEAKER_00] Čim si postaviš ta pitanja, ti razgovarar s Bogom?

46
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:39,680
[SPEAKER_00] Boga možeš naći samo na onim putovima gdje On jest.

47
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] A to su putevi duha.

48
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako tražiš, što ćeš povesti, što ćeš popiti,

49
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] pa ideš od jedne pekare do druge,

50
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:51,180
[SPEAKER_00] pa od jednog šopjeka do drugog, nigdje Isusa nećeš pronaći.

51
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:55,080
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se baviš malim niskim mislima,

52
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] ako sad misliš kako da se ja oslobodim, ne znam ja bolesti,

53
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako da je ovo, Isusa nećeš nigdje naći.

54
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:05,879
[SPEAKER_00] Ako Isusa tražiš među ljudima, njega tu nema.

55
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:12,280
[SPEAKER_00] Samo se malo podigni.

56
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] Samo se malo sjeti, tko to upravlja mojim životom?

57
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:21,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ja nisam sam mogao odrediti kad ću se roditi?

58
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:26,759
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto nisam sam mogao odrediti koji ću spol biti muško ili žensko?

59
00:04:26,759 --> 00:04:31,319
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto ja nisam mogao odrediti, hoću li biti Kinez, Japanac ili Hrvata?

60
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto ja ne mogu odrediti kad ću umrijeti?

61
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:37,939
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto ja ne znam što će biti posle moje smrti?

62
00:04:37,939 --> 00:04:42,160
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto ja ne mogu odrediti hoću li sutra biti zdrav ili bolesan?

63
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:42,759
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

64
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ja sebi ne mogu uzeti sutrašnji dan?

65
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:52,379
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto ne mogu skočiti u jučerašnji dan?

66
00:04:54,420 --> 00:04:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] Slušao sam ja tako nemoćan.

67
00:04:55,759 --> 00:05:02,639
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo mi normalno da se okreneš natrag i skočiš u jučerašnji dan i evo te u srijedi.

68
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:04,399
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaš kako kiša pada.

69
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:07,699
[SPEAKER_00] Pratila mi od splita do ovde, sve do dva u noći.

70
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:11,680
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto ne mogu skočiti u sutrašnji dan?

71
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] U petak kaže, evo ja u petku, a vi kad stignete.

72
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:16,540
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš.

73
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:19,360
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto smo tako okovani vremenom?

74
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ti možeš samo biti sada.

75
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] 20 minuta, 20 sati i 32 minuta.

76
00:05:25,899 --> 00:05:27,060
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš biti samo sada.

77
00:05:27,060 --> 00:05:30,259
[SPEAKER_00] I vrijeme te nosi svake sekunde naprijed.

78
00:05:30,259 --> 00:05:31,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ti ne možeš i naprijed i natrag.

79
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:32,160
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

80
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:36,259
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto smo tako sapiti?

81
00:05:36,259 --> 00:05:39,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ti opće ne možeš iskočiti iz jedne minute.

82
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš reći, ja hoću sad biti u jutru.

83
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,959
[SPEAKER_00] Ja hoću sad biti u podne, neka zvoni.

84
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu zvoniti sva zvona i katedrale i sve, ali nije podne.

85
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ćete li da postoje prostor u kojima Boga možeš susresti?

86
00:05:56,519 --> 00:06:00,560
[SPEAKER_00] Nećeš ga susresti u malim, sitnim svojim čarkama,

87
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,439
[SPEAKER_00] svojim malim, sitnim problemčićima,

88
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:04,240
[SPEAKER_00] u malo sitnom svom hodanju zemljom.

89
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, tu ga nema.

90
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:09,660
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što ne možeš sunce susresti,

91
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:11,240
[SPEAKER_00] ako da ideš od shoppinga do shoppinga,

92
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,360
[SPEAKER_00] pa da gledaš, ne znam ja, od jednog auta do drugoga,

93
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa da gledaš od jednog jezera do drugog.

94
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moraš pogledati i gore,

95
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] o, Bog sunce, kako si?

96
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,740
[SPEAKER_00] Nećeš drugačije sresti, Bog.

97
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] Mena je frapirala ona anegdota

98
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] kada je čovjek jadan iz istočne Njemačke

99
00:06:32,019 --> 00:06:33,879
[SPEAKER_00] došao u komunizmu, trpio užasno,

100
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:37,759
[SPEAKER_00] onda je pobjegao preko zida Berlinskoga

101
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:39,600
[SPEAKER_00] u zapadni Berlin

102
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,540
[SPEAKER_00] i uspio, ovi su pucali na njega,

103
00:06:41,540 --> 00:06:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali nisu ga ubili.

104
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:46,540
[SPEAKER_00] I dok je sjedio u karitasu u zapadnom Berlinu

105
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:49,439
[SPEAKER_00] na onom kauču i gledao ispred sebe,

106
00:06:49,439 --> 00:06:52,300
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže, padnemo upravo pred oči Isusov križ.

107
00:06:52,300 --> 00:06:55,120
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se sjeti da je od doma ostavio

108
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,759
[SPEAKER_00] djecu jadnu, gladnu i žednu,

109
00:06:56,759 --> 00:06:59,060
[SPEAKER_00] ženu koja se boji, o, će li muž ostati živ?

110
00:06:59,060 --> 00:07:01,660
[SPEAKER_00] Da je sav bio odrpan, od kiše mokar,

111
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] na nogama odrpane i stare cipele,

112
00:07:05,660 --> 00:07:10,100
[SPEAKER_00] sav jadan, od straha i užasa,

113
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:13,120
[SPEAKER_00] isprebijan i izmučen i drhti.

114
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,139
[SPEAKER_00] I onda samo pokleda Krista i kaže,

115
00:07:15,139 --> 00:07:17,360
[SPEAKER_00] ma od čega si nas ti to Kriste odkupio?

116
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] Svati da Bog nije došao da ti skuha kavu.

117
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nije došao da ti opere zube na večer.

118
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:35,439
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nije došao da ide mjesto tebe na posao,

119
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa da ti zaradi 3000 kuna,

120
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,899
[SPEAKER_00] pa da si kupiš cipele, sandale,

121
00:07:39,899 --> 00:07:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] da onduliraš kosu,

122
00:07:42,139 --> 00:07:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] pa da u parfumeriji kupiš nove šminke.

123
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome, ako na krivim putima tražiš Boga,

124
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] nikad ga naći, nećeš.

125
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:54,339
[SPEAKER_00] A te isti je čovjek koji ne zna gdje se Boga može naći.

126
00:07:54,339 --> 00:07:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ali čim upitaš sebe,

127
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,600
[SPEAKER_00] ko sam ja?

128
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] To ti nijedan čovjek nema odgovora,

129
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,839
[SPEAKER_00] sredstit ćeš samo njega.

130
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:06,560
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ti si me morao pronaći.

131
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,560
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si me stavio u trbu moje majke.

132
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,139
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, jedino ti znaš,

133
00:08:10,139 --> 00:08:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] postoji li nešto iza smrti.

134
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:13,720
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, jedino se na tebe mogu osloniti,

135
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako hoću se osloboditi krivica i muka.

136
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:18,759
[SPEAKER_00] Jedino na tebe se mogu osloniti,

137
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:22,100
[SPEAKER_00] ako znam da li ću sutra živjeti i preživjeti.

138
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:22,959
[SPEAKER_00] Nema drugoga.

139
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:24,879
[SPEAKER_00] I tad počinješ biti vjernik.

140
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] Lako je biti vjernik,

141
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:28,339
[SPEAKER_00] samo ako si dovoljno pametan.

142
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] A mi većinom radimo tako,

143
00:08:35,059 --> 00:08:36,100
[SPEAKER_00] da dođeš u neku crkvu,

144
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] pa da malo poklikneš,

145
00:08:36,980 --> 00:08:37,700
[SPEAKER_00] uzme malo svete vode,

146
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:38,240
[SPEAKER_00] pa se pekreniš.

147
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:40,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, ja bio u crkvi.

148
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] Pa bio si u crkvi.

149
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja si bio s Bogom?

150
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, da, nisi.

151
00:08:43,179 --> 00:08:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] Može ti doći susjedi

152
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] i onda pozvoniti,

153
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] ona ti otvori,

154
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] dobro dan, dobro jutro,

155
00:08:51,059 --> 00:08:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] uzeti od nje malo kruha,

156
00:08:51,980 --> 00:08:52,379
[SPEAKER_00] dobro jutro,

157
00:08:52,379 --> 00:08:52,600
[SPEAKER_00] dobro jutro,

158
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,620
[SPEAKER_00] i izleteti van.

159
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:55,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, što smo se narazgovarali,

160
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] ja i susjeda.

161
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,799
[SPEAKER_00] Baš jeste.

162
00:08:57,799 --> 00:09:00,879
[SPEAKER_00] Trebala te poslati na psihijatriju.

163
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:04,600
[SPEAKER_00] baš na psihijatriju slati

164
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] kad ovako rade u crkvi.

165
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] U crkvu kad dolaziš,

166
00:09:08,820 --> 00:09:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] onda moraš znati.

167
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,700
[SPEAKER_00] Kad dođeš liječnik,

168
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:11,399
[SPEAKER_00] onda ne dođeš tamo,

169
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:11,700
[SPEAKER_00] pa kažeš,

170
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] molim vas,

171
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,320
[SPEAKER_00] komadić kruha i tri sira

172
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] i dvoje cipele.

173
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] Pa liječniku se ne ide za to.

174
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome,

175
00:09:20,039 --> 00:09:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] kad tražiš Boga,

176
00:09:20,860 --> 00:09:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] onda moraš od nas sjetiti.

177
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:24,799
[SPEAKER_00] O tebi zavisi moja sudbina.

178
00:09:24,799 --> 00:09:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] Samo ti možeš oprosjeti moje grijehe.

179
00:09:28,139 --> 00:09:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] Samo sam zbog tebe došao na svijet.

180
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,600
[SPEAKER_00] I samo ti znaš

181
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,580
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ovaj svijet ovako?

182
00:09:33,580 --> 00:09:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] Nikko ne zna,

183
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,620
[SPEAKER_00] nikakva znanost ne zna.

184
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:36,759
[SPEAKER_00] Što je to svijet?

185
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:37,700
[SPEAKER_00] Tko sam to ja?

186
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto moram živjeti?

187
00:09:39,019 --> 00:09:40,720
[SPEAKER_00] Šta će biti s ovi šest milijardi ljudi?

188
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je naša sudbina sutra?

189
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko.

190
00:09:43,179 --> 00:09:46,019
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ga nađeš.

191
00:09:46,019 --> 00:09:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

192
00:09:46,940 --> 00:09:47,639
[SPEAKER_00] Bog, evo ja.

193
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa je lako naći.

194
00:09:50,019 --> 00:09:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] Samo ako ga tražiš

195
00:09:51,779 --> 00:09:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] na pravim putevima.

196
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:54,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, probajte ga naći.

197
00:10:01,700 --> 00:10:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] baš da vidim da li ćete ga naći.

198
00:10:04,419 --> 00:10:06,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ne, ja ću mu reći.

199
00:10:06,139 --> 00:10:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da ste ga tražili.

200
00:10:09,059 --> 00:10:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] Bit će mu drago.

201
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste uspjeli što god.

202
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jedni spavaju,

203
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] drugi su se zamislili,

204
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] treći nedostali.

205
00:10:32,399 --> 00:10:33,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, nije te tako.

206
00:10:33,779 --> 00:10:35,120
[SPEAKER_00] Tu moraš Isusa tražiti

207
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] ako hoćeš kad susred si.

208
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] I moraš znati

209
00:10:37,659 --> 00:10:40,620
[SPEAKER_00] da je Isus u povijesi čovečanstva

210
00:10:40,620 --> 00:10:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] jedini, jedini

211
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,139
[SPEAKER_00] opraštao grijehe.

212
00:10:44,139 --> 00:10:46,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jedini pokazao da ima vlast

213
00:10:46,139 --> 00:10:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] nad zlim duhovima,

214
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] nad ribama,

215
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] i biljkama,

216
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] i životinjama,

217
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,679
[SPEAKER_00] i nad morem,

218
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] i nad smrću.

219
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:53,320
[SPEAKER_00] Jedini u povijesi čovečanstva,

220
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,580
[SPEAKER_00] i nad svakom bolestu.

221
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:58,200
[SPEAKER_00] Jedini u povijesi čovečanstva

222
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] pokazao da ima vlast

223
00:10:59,659 --> 00:11:00,179
[SPEAKER_00] nad svijetom,

224
00:11:00,179 --> 00:11:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] vlasnik svijeta,

225
00:11:01,659 --> 00:11:02,919
[SPEAKER_00] prirode i svemira.

226
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jedini.

227
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:06,700
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što nam ne zna nitko,

228
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:07,759
[SPEAKER_00] nikakva znanost ne zna,

229
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] gdje smo mi to u svemiru?

230
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] Izgubljeni?

231
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:13,399
[SPEAKER_00] Što nam znanost ne zna,

232
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:14,299
[SPEAKER_00] što je to smrt?

233
00:11:14,299 --> 00:11:15,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa.

234
00:11:15,019 --> 00:11:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znanost ne zna,

235
00:11:18,019 --> 00:11:19,779
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ja moram živjeti?

236
00:11:19,779 --> 00:11:21,639
[SPEAKER_00] Odakle sam sišao na ovu zemlju?

237
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:22,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa ne zna.

238
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto toliko zla i ratova na svijetu?

239
00:11:29,179 --> 00:11:29,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa.

240
00:11:29,679 --> 00:11:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] Znanost ne zna.

241
00:11:31,519 --> 00:11:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto čovjek hoda na dvije noge?

242
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ne na četiri?

243
00:11:34,139 --> 00:11:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ne na šest kotača?

244
00:11:35,899 --> 00:11:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto baš ne dvije noge?

245
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ima dvije ruke?

246
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,200
[SPEAKER_00] Dva oka?

247
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ništa ne znamo.

248
00:11:43,019 --> 00:11:44,299
[SPEAKER_00] I samo znamo da je to tako.

249
00:11:44,299 --> 00:11:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] Znanost samo kaže da to je tako i točka.

250
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,919
[SPEAKER_00] Znanost vam ništa ne koristi za život.

251
00:11:48,919 --> 00:11:51,360
[SPEAKER_00] I zato moraš tražiti samo jednoga

252
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] koji to zna,

253
00:11:52,059 --> 00:11:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] vlasnika prirode,

254
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] svemira i tebe.

255
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] Sve kad pita od koje tebi načinio

256
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] tvoju ruku i tvoje lice,

257
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] tko ti je dao tvoju kosu?

258
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dok to ne rešiš,

259
00:12:05,340 --> 00:12:06,419
[SPEAKER_00] nikad Boga nećeš naći.

260
00:12:06,419 --> 00:12:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pita je mamu,

261
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] mama, jesi ti mene dala ruku?

262
00:12:10,059 --> 00:12:10,580
[SPEAKER_00] Pa će reći,

263
00:12:10,580 --> 00:12:11,200
[SPEAKER_00] djete moje,

264
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne pravim ruke.

265
00:12:12,519 --> 00:12:14,759
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tko onda pravi,

266
00:12:14,759 --> 00:12:15,179
[SPEAKER_00] jel tata?

267
00:12:15,179 --> 00:12:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ha, tata, ne zna,

268
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:16,799
[SPEAKER_00] ni noge napravili,

269
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] kamoli ruke.

270
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tko mi je glavu napravio?

271
00:12:21,539 --> 00:12:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ha, da.

272
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,320
[SPEAKER_00] Tražili smo liječnika,

273
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,740
[SPEAKER_00] pa je došla tri kirurga,

274
00:12:24,740 --> 00:12:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] pa su ti napravili glavu, jel?

275
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tko pravi glave naše?

276
00:12:28,019 --> 00:12:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] Tko mozak sa milijardu stanica?

277
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] ko to pravi mozgove ljudi?

278
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:36,740
[SPEAKER_00] Tko će to danas,

279
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:37,940
[SPEAKER_00] sto tisuća djeca,

280
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:39,379
[SPEAKER_00] poslati na ovaj svijet?

281
00:12:39,379 --> 00:12:41,419
[SPEAKER_00] Tko je to napravio,

282
00:12:41,419 --> 00:12:42,580
[SPEAKER_00] tako je savršenstvo,

283
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:44,399
[SPEAKER_00] čovjekovog organizma?

284
00:12:44,399 --> 00:12:49,799
[SPEAKER_00] Čim siđate na tu razinu

285
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] i samo se podsjetite,

286
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:52,360
[SPEAKER_00] tu je netko,

287
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:52,919
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćeš shvatiti,

288
00:12:52,919 --> 00:12:54,279
[SPEAKER_00] o, on je mene stvorio,

289
00:12:54,279 --> 00:12:55,580
[SPEAKER_00] ova ruka je od njega.

290
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,379
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

291
00:12:56,379 --> 00:12:57,720
[SPEAKER_00] ova ruka je trag

292
00:12:58,299 --> 00:13:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] Isusove prisutnosti.

293
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,120
[SPEAKER_00] On je jedini Bog.

294
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] On me stvorio.

295
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:04,879
[SPEAKER_00] On je savršeni menedžer.

296
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] On je izvrstni inženjer.

297
00:13:06,559 --> 00:13:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] Samo je on to načinio.

298
00:13:08,820 --> 00:13:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] I on je vlasnik.

299
00:13:10,179 --> 00:13:11,200
[SPEAKER_00] I on je gospodar.

300
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:11,779
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

301
00:13:11,779 --> 00:13:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] k njemu trebamo ići.

302
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:16,419
[SPEAKER_00] To je to što trebate.

303
00:13:16,419 --> 00:13:18,100
[SPEAKER_00] Mi stalno negdje lupamo

304
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] na kriva vrata

305
00:13:18,940 --> 00:13:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

306
00:13:19,259 --> 00:13:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] nema Boga.

307
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] Onda molimo tri zdravo Marije,

308
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] a Isus kaže,

309
00:13:22,759 --> 00:13:23,740
[SPEAKER_00] nisam ja zdravo Marija,

310
00:13:23,740 --> 00:13:24,860
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam Isus.

311
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:27,600
[SPEAKER_00] Onda brže mi oče naš,

312
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,379
[SPEAKER_00] koji je sran besmanješka,

313
00:13:28,379 --> 00:13:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] nisam ja oče naš.

314
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam opet Isus.

315
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,759
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako sad?

316
00:13:31,759 --> 00:13:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] U imeca Sine dva svijeta kaže,

317
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] nisam ja ni to.

318
00:13:33,759 --> 00:13:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tko si ti Isus?

319
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] E, ja sam Isus.

320
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je Isus?

321
00:13:38,980 --> 00:13:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onaj koji ti je dao ruku.

322
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Po meni je sve stvoreno.

323
00:13:44,919 --> 00:13:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj koji drži ovo cvijeće

324
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] da postoji.

325
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:49,100
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj koji drži atomsku energiju

326
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:49,919
[SPEAKER_00] i svaku energiju.

327
00:13:49,919 --> 00:13:51,299
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste napravili struju.

328
00:13:51,299 --> 00:13:53,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ja držim zakone struje

329
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] u svojoj ruci,

330
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] kaže Isus.

331
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam gospodar svega.

332
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam menedžer.

333
00:13:59,159 --> 00:14:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam sve načinio.

334
00:14:00,039 --> 00:14:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] I kad tog se sjetiš,

335
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] vidiš kako ti brzo dolazi

336
00:14:04,759 --> 00:14:06,059
[SPEAKER_00] Isus ovog pogleda.

337
00:14:06,059 --> 00:14:06,740
[SPEAKER_00] Bržeš ga naći.

338
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] I joj, Isuse, pa gdje si?

339
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

340
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] Jer dok tako razmišljaš,

341
00:14:10,159 --> 00:14:12,379
[SPEAKER_00] u tebi se otvaraju prostori duha.

342
00:14:12,379 --> 00:14:12,879
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite.

343
00:14:14,379 --> 00:14:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno je očima vidjeti.

344
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:18,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš glazbu vidjeti.

345
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,919
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno je ušima slušati.

346
00:14:19,919 --> 00:14:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš svjetlo slušati.

347
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:25,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno je rukama pipati.

348
00:14:25,139 --> 00:14:26,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš svjetlo pipati,

349
00:14:26,779 --> 00:14:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] niti glas pipati.

350
00:14:29,059 --> 00:14:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš samo to pipati,

351
00:14:31,159 --> 00:14:31,919
[SPEAKER_00] nešto što je to rado.

352
00:14:31,919 --> 00:14:33,899
[SPEAKER_00] Pratom imamo različite sposobnosti.

353
00:14:34,299 --> 00:14:35,620
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi smo Boga prepoznali,

354
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:36,740
[SPEAKER_00] trebaš sposobnost duha,

355
00:14:36,740 --> 00:14:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] intelekta.

356
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:39,720
[SPEAKER_00] I kad to shvatiš,

357
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] biće ti lako da Isusa dođe.

358
00:14:41,159 --> 00:14:45,700
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto su ljudi ateisti?

359
00:14:45,700 --> 00:14:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što pod svaku cijenu

360
00:14:47,259 --> 00:14:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] hoće vidjeti pjesmu na CD-u.

361
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:52,639
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš samo ti gledaj.

362
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nemaj.

363
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:58,179
[SPEAKER_00] Moraš slušati.

364
00:14:58,179 --> 00:14:59,600
[SPEAKER_00] Zatvori oči i slušaj,

365
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:01,679
[SPEAKER_00] a ne otvori oči i gledaj glazbu.

366
00:15:01,679 --> 00:15:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] To je jako važno.

367
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:05,700
[SPEAKER_00] Zato, dakle,

368
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] vi morate odmah se svjetiti.

369
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:08,620
[SPEAKER_00] Kositi Isusa.

370
00:15:08,620 --> 00:15:09,659
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte.

371
00:15:09,659 --> 00:15:10,919
[SPEAKER_00] O tebe je to.

372
00:15:10,919 --> 00:15:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Krasno.

373
00:15:13,519 --> 00:15:14,700
[SPEAKER_00] Da je tako lako došli do Isusa.

374
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:16,899
[SPEAKER_00] Pita mi,

375
00:15:16,899 --> 00:15:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću u Splitu,

376
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:18,700
[SPEAKER_00] a kako vi to do Isusa došli?

377
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa rekao,

378
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] prijednik sam došao u Split.

379
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam došao u sobi

380
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] svoje kapeljice.

381
00:15:22,019 --> 00:15:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] Lijepo došao,

382
00:15:23,159 --> 00:15:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] da slonio se na štok

383
00:15:24,139 --> 00:15:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] i kažem,

384
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,639
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa, ja ti idem u Split.

385
00:15:25,639 --> 00:15:27,799
[SPEAKER_00] Gleda on mene,

386
00:15:27,799 --> 00:15:28,320
[SPEAKER_00] ja njega.

387
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kod mene u tabernakulu.

388
00:15:30,559 --> 00:15:30,980
[SPEAKER_00] I on rekao,

389
00:15:30,980 --> 00:15:32,179
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa, ćemo skupa.

390
00:15:32,179 --> 00:15:33,879
[SPEAKER_00] Nego šta, kaže on,

391
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] idemo.

392
00:15:34,179 --> 00:15:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] I onda smo krenuli,

393
00:15:36,019 --> 00:15:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] rekao, ja vam tamo govoriti.

394
00:15:37,039 --> 00:15:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, ti?

395
00:15:37,820 --> 00:15:45,919
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je jednostavno.

396
00:15:45,919 --> 00:15:47,419
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si ti na pravoj razini,

397
00:15:47,419 --> 00:15:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] na razini duha,

398
00:15:48,139 --> 00:15:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] ti možeš s Bogom uvijek razgovarati.

399
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:52,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako si na psihofizičkoj razini,

400
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:54,820
[SPEAKER_00] a ako ćeš na istoj razini

401
00:15:54,820 --> 00:15:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] na kojoj učeš biologiju,

402
00:15:56,519 --> 00:15:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] kemiju i fiziku,

403
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] na toj razini vidjeti Boga.

404
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,059
[SPEAKER_00] Nema ga.

405
00:15:59,059 --> 00:16:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] Uzalud je to.

406
00:16:00,019 --> 00:16:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dođeš na crkvu,

407
00:16:03,340 --> 00:16:04,120
[SPEAKER_00] gledaš na tabernakulu,

408
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] nigdje Isusa kaže.

409
00:16:05,059 --> 00:16:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] Sada će niko tvrti tabernakulu,

410
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,139
[SPEAKER_00] nema ga ni tamo.

411
00:16:08,139 --> 00:16:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] Pa gdje je Isus?

412
00:16:08,779 --> 00:16:13,259
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sad je da ne možeš

413
00:16:13,259 --> 00:16:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] misao vidjeti u očima.

414
00:16:14,659 --> 00:16:15,179
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš stano,

415
00:16:15,179 --> 00:16:16,279
[SPEAKER_00] ako ja sad kažem,

416
00:16:16,279 --> 00:16:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] ti si čovjek,

417
00:16:17,279 --> 00:16:17,659
[SPEAKER_00] da gledaš,

418
00:16:17,659 --> 00:16:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je to ti si čovjek?

419
00:16:18,779 --> 00:16:20,120
[SPEAKER_00] Nigde to je misli.

420
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:20,740
[SPEAKER_00] Sto li gdje vidjeli?

421
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:21,259
[SPEAKER_00] Nema je.

422
00:16:21,259 --> 00:16:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] A svatko je od vas razumio

423
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:25,100
[SPEAKER_00] i vidi tu misao.

424
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si čovjek.

425
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nevidljivo očima

426
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:30,879
[SPEAKER_00] ne ču na misao,

427
00:16:30,879 --> 00:16:31,659
[SPEAKER_00] se ne može čuti,

428
00:16:31,659 --> 00:16:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne može se pipati,

429
00:16:32,460 --> 00:16:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] ne može se mirisati.

430
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] A sima jasno,

431
00:16:34,639 --> 00:16:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] ti si čovjek.

432
00:16:35,159 --> 00:16:36,840
[SPEAKER_00] Čuo sam tu,

433
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:37,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali misao je izašla

434
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] iz toga glasa.

435
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:40,080
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam čuo glasa,

436
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:40,620
[SPEAKER_00] ne misao.

437
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:41,580
[SPEAKER_00] Misao se ne može čuti.

438
00:16:41,580 --> 00:16:45,139
[SPEAKER_00] Vi kao saudenti,

439
00:16:45,139 --> 00:16:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] morate to jedan put

440
00:16:45,740 --> 00:16:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] poznavati.

441
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto vi vjerujete u Boga?

442
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se to vjeruju u Boga?

443
00:16:48,940 --> 00:16:50,419
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi toliko lutaju.

444
00:16:50,419 --> 00:16:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ga je sa čega pravi.

445
00:16:52,460 --> 00:16:53,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znači kako bake kaže,

446
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,179
[SPEAKER_00] a sinko, dragi,

447
00:16:54,179 --> 00:16:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] molim si krunica,

448
00:16:55,059 --> 00:16:56,080
[SPEAKER_00] što ja znam gdje je Bog.

449
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:57,240
[SPEAKER_00] Bako, drago,

450
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,179
[SPEAKER_00] ja bi njega ti ovidjeti.

451
00:16:58,179 --> 00:16:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] E, je, puno ćeš se mučiti.

452
00:16:59,639 --> 00:17:00,379
[SPEAKER_00] Ostarila ja,

453
00:17:00,379 --> 00:17:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] nigdje Boga.

454
00:17:01,019 --> 00:17:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ali gospod sam nekako našla.

455
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zdravo Mario,

456
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:04,680
[SPEAKER_00] sveta Mario.

457
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] Stvare su sasvim jednostavne.

458
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] Čim počemo biti razumni,

459
00:17:13,019 --> 00:17:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] trijezni i tako dalje.

460
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:18,359
[SPEAKER_00] A te iznam je po sebi samo teška bolest.

461
00:17:18,359 --> 00:17:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] To je nesporazum i ništa drugo.

462
00:17:20,619 --> 00:17:26,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ti ste čovjek koji hoće silom slušati očima glazbu.

463
00:17:26,700 --> 00:17:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Samo se podsjetite na te unutra.

464
00:17:31,460 --> 00:17:32,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ma tako je bliz Isus.

465
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:36,839
[SPEAKER_00] Sto put sam govorio na Simogljim seminariom još deset godina.

466
00:17:36,839 --> 00:17:38,700
[SPEAKER_00] Hoćeš naći Isusa, pogledaj svoju ruku.

467
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ga, on mi ovo napravio.

468
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] I oj, Isus jesi strašan.

469
00:17:42,599 --> 00:17:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ga kaže,

470
00:17:44,019 --> 00:17:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] uhvatim ga brže u ruku.

471
00:17:45,019 --> 00:17:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] Evo Isusa.

472
00:17:45,599 --> 00:17:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sa mnom je.

473
00:17:47,599 --> 00:17:49,160
[SPEAKER_00] To će ni problem.

474
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] Opipan svoje lice,

475
00:17:51,559 --> 00:17:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] ti si mi ga dao.

476
00:17:52,539 --> 00:17:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ga, Isus je tu.

477
00:17:54,599 --> 00:17:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne vidite ga.

478
00:17:55,539 --> 00:17:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je žao.

479
00:17:57,480 --> 00:18:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoj tražiti na krivim putevima

480
00:18:01,579 --> 00:18:03,279
[SPEAKER_00] onoga koji je na pravom putu.

481
00:18:03,279 --> 00:18:07,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, probajte još jedan put.

482
00:18:07,140 --> 00:18:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] Oćete?

483
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,259
[SPEAKER_00] Mora da je to pronaći,

484
00:18:09,259 --> 00:18:10,740
[SPEAKER_00] jer ćemo vam vaši fakulteti,

485
00:18:10,740 --> 00:18:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] ako niste naučili kako se Boga pronalazi,

486
00:18:13,599 --> 00:18:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] kako s njima druguje,

487
00:18:14,559 --> 00:18:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] kako s njima možeš se smijati.

488
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:17,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, probajte.

489
00:18:24,059 --> 00:18:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] Niko ne glada svoju ruku.

490
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:27,180
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ćete vidjeti Boga ako ne gladaš ruku?

491
00:18:27,180 --> 00:18:28,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ja moram pogledati dlajem i kažem,

492
00:18:28,720 --> 00:18:30,319
[SPEAKER_00] još što si dobro napravio.

493
00:18:30,319 --> 00:18:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jer znam,

494
00:18:32,619 --> 00:18:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] niko mi to nije dao.

495
00:18:33,900 --> 00:18:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam sam napravio svoju ruku.

496
00:18:35,559 --> 00:18:36,720
[SPEAKER_00] Nije niko,

497
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] ni liječnici,

498
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:38,359
[SPEAKER_00] ni želja.

499
00:18:38,359 --> 00:18:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] Niko mi nije napravio ruku.

500
00:18:39,619 --> 00:18:40,059
[SPEAKER_00] Niko znam,

501
00:18:40,059 --> 00:18:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] ti si to.

502
00:18:41,279 --> 00:18:42,759
[SPEAKER_00] I to je tako jasan znak.

503
00:18:42,759 --> 00:18:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kakav onaj musliman bio

504
00:18:45,519 --> 00:18:47,640
[SPEAKER_00] sa jednim znanstvenikom

505
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,799
[SPEAKER_00] koji praučavao pustinju.

506
00:18:48,799 --> 00:18:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] Bili su u pustinji zajedno.

507
00:18:53,859 --> 00:18:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kaže,

508
00:18:54,759 --> 00:18:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] ujutro rano još prije izlaska sunca

509
00:18:56,579 --> 00:18:58,799
[SPEAKER_00] eno musliman kleči ispred šatora

510
00:18:58,799 --> 00:19:00,160
[SPEAKER_00] i moli.

511
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] U to dođe ovaj znanstvenik,

512
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] Engles.

513
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

514
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] što radiš?

515
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,160
[SPEAKER_00] Klanjam se.

516
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] Kome?

517
00:19:05,660 --> 00:19:06,359
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu.

518
00:19:06,359 --> 00:19:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] Pa gdje ti je Bog?

519
00:19:07,319 --> 00:19:08,759
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tu je.

520
00:19:08,759 --> 00:19:10,240
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako znaš da Bog postoji?

521
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:12,359
[SPEAKER_00] Si ga vidio niz.

522
00:19:12,359 --> 00:19:14,339
[SPEAKER_00] Pa si ga čuo niz.

523
00:19:14,339 --> 00:19:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] Si vidio njegove tragove niza.

524
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:19,180
[SPEAKER_00] Kako znaš ono da postoji Bog?

525
00:19:23,599 --> 00:19:25,640
[SPEAKER_00] U to inženjer dok je tako gleda musliman

526
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] ne zna odgovoriti.

527
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

528
00:19:27,039 --> 00:19:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako se može klaniti nekog koga ne znaš

529
00:19:28,460 --> 00:19:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] i koga ne postoji?

530
00:19:29,119 --> 00:19:30,180
[SPEAKER_00] Onda on gleda

531
00:19:30,180 --> 00:19:32,140
[SPEAKER_00] ono ispred šatora

532
00:19:32,140 --> 00:19:33,140
[SPEAKER_00] neki tragovi.

533
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:35,200
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

534
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje je netko prošao,

535
00:19:36,099 --> 00:19:36,839
[SPEAKER_00] kaže musliman.

536
00:19:36,839 --> 00:19:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kako znaš?

537
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vidim tragove deve

538
00:19:39,460 --> 00:19:41,299
[SPEAKER_00] i dva čovjeka.

539
00:19:41,299 --> 00:19:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] Možno su dva vodiča

540
00:19:42,460 --> 00:19:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] i deva proći.

541
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako znaš?

542
00:19:44,099 --> 00:19:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vidim tragove.

543
00:19:45,079 --> 00:19:47,720
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako?

544
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne vidiš ljude?

545
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:48,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

546
00:19:48,740 --> 00:19:49,720
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vidim tragove.

547
00:19:50,859 --> 00:19:51,799
[SPEAKER_00] U to je upravo izlazilo

548
00:19:51,799 --> 00:19:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] jutarnje sunce.

549
00:19:52,740 --> 00:19:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] A musliman pogleda

550
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:55,640
[SPEAKER_00] u jutarnje sunce

551
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:55,819
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže

552
00:19:55,819 --> 00:19:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] enoga.

553
00:19:56,579 --> 00:19:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što kaže?

554
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] Traga.

555
00:19:58,859 --> 00:19:59,799
[SPEAKER_00] Koga?

556
00:19:59,799 --> 00:20:00,400
[SPEAKER_00] Boga.

557
00:20:01,660 --> 00:20:02,799
[SPEAKER_00] Evo zašto mu se klanja.

558
00:20:02,799 --> 00:20:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kako znaš da postoji Boga?

559
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:09,220
[SPEAKER_00] Evo traga.

560
00:20:09,220 --> 00:20:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] Sunce.

561
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] Eno traga.

562
00:20:12,220 --> 00:20:15,359
[SPEAKER_00] Zvijeze.

563
00:20:15,359 --> 00:20:16,160
[SPEAKER_00] Eno traga.

564
00:20:21,539 --> 00:20:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jel vi šta razumijete?

565
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Morate malo naoštriti pamet.

566
00:20:25,539 --> 00:20:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nećete stići daleko.

567
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jel vi znate da vi osim razuma,

568
00:20:33,420 --> 00:20:34,259
[SPEAKER_00] osim racija,

569
00:20:34,259 --> 00:20:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] imate i intelekt?

570
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:38,359
[SPEAKER_00] Da razum vidi samo

571
00:20:38,359 --> 00:20:39,720
[SPEAKER_00] od prilike do ovde,

572
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] a intelekt vidi preko.

573
00:20:41,079 --> 00:20:44,740
[SPEAKER_00] Jel vi znate da razum

574
00:20:44,740 --> 00:20:46,160
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš praviti filozofiju,

575
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] a intelektom možeš?

576
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:49,759
[SPEAKER_00] Jel vi znate da razum

577
00:20:49,759 --> 00:20:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] ne vidi vrednote

578
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] da moraš biti dobar.

579
00:20:52,380 --> 00:20:54,180
[SPEAKER_00] To se razumski ne može vidjeti.

580
00:20:54,180 --> 00:20:55,640
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš raspragati cijeli dan

581
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] da je dobro biti dobar.

582
00:20:56,519 --> 00:20:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] Nije kaže,

583
00:20:56,819 --> 00:20:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] no je bolje biti zločest.

584
00:20:57,980 --> 00:20:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tako razum.

585
00:20:59,039 --> 00:21:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] Razum je strašno glup.

586
00:21:00,119 --> 00:21:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ali intelektu je tako jasno.

587
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pošten biti,

588
00:21:04,980 --> 00:21:05,839
[SPEAKER_00] ti si vječan.

589
00:21:05,839 --> 00:21:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Biti dobar,

590
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,259
[SPEAKER_00] niko te uništit ne može.

591
00:21:08,259 --> 00:21:10,720
[SPEAKER_00] To je dakle druga sposobnost.

592
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:14,319
[SPEAKER_00] I zato što vi svi studirate,

593
00:21:14,319 --> 00:21:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam neke prirode zanose,

594
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:17,359
[SPEAKER_00] vi svi sa razumom funkcionirate.

595
00:21:17,359 --> 00:21:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] I onda vam nije intelekt proradio.

596
00:21:19,759 --> 00:21:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] Zato, morate proraditi intelektno,

597
00:21:21,380 --> 00:21:21,920
[SPEAKER_00] vidite bolje.

598
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,200
[SPEAKER_00] Da kada ste ljudi

599
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,339
[SPEAKER_00] koji sve sa ušima rade

600
00:21:24,339 --> 00:21:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] i stano žmire cijeli dan.

601
00:21:25,539 --> 00:21:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, ljudi stalno pitaju

602
00:21:27,539 --> 00:21:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je Bog.

603
00:21:28,279 --> 00:21:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] I onda stalno pitaju,

604
00:21:29,660 --> 00:21:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, kad će već jednom

605
00:21:30,380 --> 00:21:31,079
[SPEAKER_00] svanuti sunce?

606
00:21:31,079 --> 00:21:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] A stano žmire, žmire.

607
00:21:32,059 --> 00:21:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kad će već jednom svanuti sunce?

608
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ma čovječe,

609
00:21:34,119 --> 00:21:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] svanulo je davno.

610
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:37,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kad će Bog

611
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] sići među nas?

612
