829
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] Oni koji ne dalje su zabrnuti

830
00:27:07,039 --> 00:27:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] i gledaju

831
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] i razmišljaju.

832
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] Svati da se Boga

833
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] ne dohvaća razmišljanjem.

834
00:27:12,619 --> 00:27:14,299
[SPEAKER_00] Razmišljanjem je dohvaćaš

835
00:27:14,299 --> 00:27:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] samo svoju mislu,

836
00:27:15,559 --> 00:27:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne Boga.

837
00:27:16,319 --> 00:27:17,319
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nije mislu.

838
00:27:17,319 --> 00:27:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] I nije u mislima.

839
00:27:19,519 --> 00:27:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nego upravo u tom

840
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] duh tvoj intuicijski.

841
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:24,819
[SPEAKER_00] Duh gleda u trenutku.

842
00:27:24,819 --> 00:27:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] Intuicijski prepoznaje tu je.

843
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,200
[SPEAKER_00] I tad si sretan.

844
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:32,759
[SPEAKER_00] Da Boga se ne dolazi razmišljanjem.

845
00:27:32,759 --> 00:27:33,200
[SPEAKER_00] Svati.

846
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] Samo vidiš.

847
00:27:34,519 --> 00:27:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] Uhvatiš gospodina.

848
00:27:38,539 --> 00:27:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo sada još jedan korak do Boga.

849
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] Naši susreti četvrtkom služa

850
00:27:46,799 --> 00:27:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] upravo da bismo susreli Boga.

851
00:27:48,539 --> 00:27:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi se s njime živjeli.

852
00:27:51,079 --> 00:27:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi se ga vidjeli, čuli, doživjeli.

853
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:58,240
[SPEAKER_00] I zato ovo prvo, prvi način

854
00:27:58,240 --> 00:27:59,859
[SPEAKER_00] kako ćeš Boga prepoznati.

855
00:27:59,859 --> 00:28:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, kako ćeš Boga prepoznati?

856
00:28:02,119 --> 00:28:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kad nekome oprostiš

857
00:28:05,019 --> 00:28:06,279
[SPEAKER_00] što te je povrijedio,

858
00:28:06,279 --> 00:28:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] ako mu oprostiš

859
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:09,740
[SPEAKER_00] i pokuša čitavim slice reći

860
00:28:09,740 --> 00:28:10,740
[SPEAKER_00] opraštam ti.

861
00:28:10,740 --> 00:28:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moraš ići k njemu,

862
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] nego samo u sebi reći

863
00:28:13,759 --> 00:28:15,299
[SPEAKER_00] opraštam ti, razumijem te,

864
00:28:15,299 --> 00:28:16,799
[SPEAKER_00] ne dam da me zlo zahvati

865
00:28:16,799 --> 00:28:17,680
[SPEAKER_00] iz tebe.

866
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] Opraštam ti.

867
00:28:18,779 --> 00:28:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] To ćeš osjetiti isto blizinu Božu.

868
00:28:21,420 --> 00:28:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ako se odlučiš

869
00:28:24,779 --> 00:28:26,640
[SPEAKER_00] da ćeš biti dobar.

870
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ako kažeš

871
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] žao mi je što sam dosad bio zločest

872
00:28:29,279 --> 00:28:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] i zao što sam psovao,

873
00:28:30,579 --> 00:28:31,819
[SPEAKER_00] ogovarao, ljenčario,

874
00:28:31,819 --> 00:28:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] bludničio,

875
00:28:33,119 --> 00:28:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] krao i tako dalje.

876
00:28:34,380 --> 00:28:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] Žao mi je.

877
00:28:35,099 --> 00:28:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se odlučiš od sad,

878
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] želim biti drugačiji.

879
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] Želim biti pošten,

880
00:28:38,980 --> 00:28:40,640
[SPEAKER_00] čestit, pravedan čovjek.

881
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] Čim te okažeš,

882
00:28:43,140 --> 00:28:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Boga ćeš odmah susresti.

883
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

884
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jer činiti grijeh

885
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,160
[SPEAKER_00] znači

886
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] uništavati svoje sposobnosti.

887
00:28:50,799 --> 00:28:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] Vi znate da

888
00:28:52,380 --> 00:28:54,180
[SPEAKER_00] neurologija tako jasno kaže,

889
00:28:54,180 --> 00:28:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] čim rekneš negativnu riječ,

890
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] ti si već uništio nekoliko stanica svoga mozga.

891
00:28:58,380 --> 00:29:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] I nesposoban si vidjeti stvari.

892
00:29:00,519 --> 00:29:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se opredjeluješ za dobro,

893
00:29:05,539 --> 00:29:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] za pozitivno,

894
00:29:06,460 --> 00:29:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] za čestito,

895
00:29:07,099 --> 00:29:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] mozak se rehabilitira.

896
00:29:11,319 --> 00:29:12,200
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i onaj dio mozga

897
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:13,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji si uništio drogom,

898
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] alkoholom

899
00:29:14,119 --> 00:29:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] i koji je čim drugim.

900
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] I budući dakle,

901
00:29:18,079 --> 00:29:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je Bog uvijek

902
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno biće,

903
00:29:20,019 --> 00:29:20,359
[SPEAKER_00] zato,

904
00:29:20,359 --> 00:29:22,339
[SPEAKER_00] čim se opredjeluješ za dobro,

905
00:29:22,339 --> 00:29:23,700
[SPEAKER_00] tada i tvoj mozak,

906
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] i sve tvoje sposobnosti su

907
00:29:25,039 --> 00:29:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] izvrsne,

908
00:29:26,579 --> 00:29:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] vrsne,

909
00:29:27,220 --> 00:29:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] dakle vrhunske,

910
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] i zato možeš Boga sresti.

911
00:29:29,380 --> 00:29:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si u zlu,

912
00:29:30,559 --> 00:29:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] tada su tvoje sposobnosti minimalne.

913
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:33,200
[SPEAKER_00] To ti je kao da

914
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] jedva vidiš ovako,

915
00:29:34,519 --> 00:29:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] li ima svijetla?

916
00:29:35,559 --> 00:29:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ima.

917
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:39,160
[SPEAKER_00] To ti je kad činiš grije.

918
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,859
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi zapravo su zatvorene oči,

919
00:29:40,859 --> 00:29:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] uništen pogled

920
00:29:41,900 --> 00:29:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] i ne možeš ništa vidjeti.

921
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] A čim se opredjeluješ za dobro,

922
00:29:47,019 --> 00:29:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] jedan puta,

923
00:29:47,279 --> 00:29:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] bu, ho.

924
00:29:48,019 --> 00:29:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan puta vidiš tamo,

925
00:29:51,819 --> 00:29:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] kao na onoj slici,

926
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:54,839
[SPEAKER_00] kako to Michelangelo kraso

927
00:29:54,839 --> 00:29:56,720
[SPEAKER_00] napravio u kapeli Sistini,

928
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:58,420
[SPEAKER_00] kako Bog pruža svoj prs,

929
00:29:58,420 --> 00:29:59,240
[SPEAKER_00] a ti polako svoj,

930
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] pa se još pružaš, pružaš.

931
00:30:00,099 --> 00:30:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus kaže,

932
00:30:01,019 --> 00:30:02,319
[SPEAKER_00] di još malo se odreci zla.

933
00:30:02,319 --> 00:30:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Di još malo.

934
00:30:03,599 --> 00:30:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] I da odirnete se.

935
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:05,759
[SPEAKER_00] A to je lijepo.

936
00:30:07,460 --> 00:30:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kada je ljubav najdraža,

937
00:30:09,119 --> 00:30:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] najsilovitija?

938
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kada svako volite,

939
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] mladići djevoke,

940
00:30:13,940 --> 00:30:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] ili kada si krad mami,

941
00:30:15,619 --> 00:30:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] ili neko ko te voli.

942
00:30:16,599 --> 00:30:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] I sam ovako malo,

943
00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:20,180
[SPEAKER_00] malim prstem dodirneš njegov mali prst.

944
00:30:20,180 --> 00:30:21,319
[SPEAKER_00] Što je to ljubav?

945
00:30:21,319 --> 00:30:23,420
[SPEAKER_00] Kada nešto plane od tebe,

946
00:30:23,420 --> 00:30:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] silovito.

947
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:26,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ono kad ga zagriješ,

948
00:30:26,740 --> 00:30:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] poljiveš, nije to.

949
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:28,700
[SPEAKER_00] Onda kada sve unišiš nekako.

950
00:30:28,700 --> 00:30:29,759
[SPEAKER_00] Boli je te leža,

951
00:30:29,759 --> 00:30:30,240
[SPEAKER_00] boli grlo,

952
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,880
[SPEAKER_00] boli te vrat,

953
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] boli ruke.

954
00:30:32,539 --> 00:30:36,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ono malo nježno to plane.

955
00:30:36,339 --> 00:30:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] čitava duša plane.

956
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:39,400
[SPEAKER_00] To je upravo to.

957
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] To je Michelangelo napravio.

958
00:30:41,380 --> 00:30:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] S ono je kratko dodirno.

959
00:30:43,519 --> 00:30:48,279
[SPEAKER_00] I to je duhovna dimenzija, vidite.

960
00:30:48,279 --> 00:30:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] Boga ne treba da čvrsto uzmiš,

961
00:30:51,119 --> 00:30:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] pa zgrabiš, pa uništiš sve.

962
00:30:52,559 --> 00:30:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje si Isuse?

963
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:54,640
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

964
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] bježmo, dečke, idu cure.

965
00:30:57,619 --> 00:30:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] Bježmo odavde,

966
00:30:58,619 --> 00:30:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] oče moju ugraviti.

967
00:30:59,619 --> 00:31:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] Nego kada ona izdaleka nježno,

968
00:31:01,539 --> 00:31:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] toplo.

969
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,099
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse.

970
00:31:03,099 --> 00:31:07,660
[SPEAKER_00] Probajte taj drugi korak.

971
00:31:07,660 --> 00:31:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oprosti nekome.

972
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] I zamoli nek se tebi oprosti.

973
00:31:14,900 --> 00:31:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, odreći se zla.

974
00:31:16,819 --> 00:31:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi u tebe ušlo dobro,

975
00:31:18,599 --> 00:31:20,240
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi tvoje oči, duše,

976
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] postale sposobne vidjeti Boga.

977
00:31:23,559 --> 00:31:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] I odluči da ćeš biti pošten,

978
00:31:25,079 --> 00:31:26,339
[SPEAKER_00] da više nećeš psovati,

979
00:31:26,339 --> 00:31:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] da nećeš krasti,

980
00:31:27,519 --> 00:31:28,819
[SPEAKER_00] da nećeš ogovarati.

981
00:31:28,819 --> 00:31:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjet ćeš kako tebi rase sposobnost.

982
00:31:31,299 --> 00:31:39,240
[SPEAKER_00] Boga se vidi na putovima sunca,

983
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:41,279
[SPEAKER_00] pravde, dobrote, ljudskosti,

984
00:31:41,279 --> 00:31:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] humanosti,

985
00:31:42,279 --> 00:31:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] čovjekoljubivosti.

986
00:31:44,539 --> 00:31:45,180
[SPEAKER_00] Samo tu.

987
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] U mržnika ne možeš vidjeti.

988
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] Mržnja je mrak,

989
00:31:49,079 --> 00:31:50,200
[SPEAKER_00] ogovaranje je mrak,

990
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,160
[SPEAKER_00] krađa je mrak,

991
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] psovka je mrak,

992
00:31:52,220 --> 00:31:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] bludnost.

993
00:31:53,559 --> 00:31:55,160
[SPEAKER_00] I tako dalje,

994
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] pravdub je mrak.

995
00:31:56,500 --> 00:31:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] Tu Boga ne možeš vidjeti.

996
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] Samo se odlučio,

997
00:32:02,619 --> 00:32:03,700
[SPEAKER_00] hoću biti pošten.

998
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] Žao mi je.

999
00:32:04,420 --> 00:32:08,839
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto desni razbojnik je vidio Isusa

1000
00:32:08,839 --> 00:32:09,640
[SPEAKER_00] i da je on Bog?

1001
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ljevi to nije vidio.

1002
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:12,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ja desni je rekao,

1003
00:32:12,299 --> 00:32:12,900
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine,

1004
00:32:12,900 --> 00:32:13,859
[SPEAKER_00] žao mi je,

1005
00:32:13,859 --> 00:32:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam grešnik.

1006
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam kriv što sam,

1007
00:32:17,019 --> 00:32:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam zaslužio da sam na križu,

1008
00:32:18,740 --> 00:32:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali ti si nevin.

1009
00:32:19,579 --> 00:32:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] Žao mi je,

1010
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse, sjeti me se,

1011
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:23,160
[SPEAKER_00] oprosti mi.

1012
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] A ono je desni vikao,

1013
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] stavi, skiniti nas križa

1014
00:32:26,039 --> 00:32:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo ono je,

1015
00:32:26,519 --> 00:32:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, pa nisam te ni stavio na križ,

1016
00:32:29,019 --> 00:32:29,700
[SPEAKER_00] šta ćete skiniti?

1017
00:32:29,700 --> 00:32:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite koliko je različite.

1018
00:32:34,539 --> 00:32:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj desni je zapravo

1019
00:32:35,940 --> 00:32:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] se uspao na razinu duha,

1020
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:38,259
[SPEAKER_00] oprosti mi.

1021
00:32:38,259 --> 00:32:39,859
[SPEAKER_00] I mogo je prepoznati

1022
00:32:39,859 --> 00:32:40,640
[SPEAKER_00] Isusu da je Bog.

1023
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj ljeve,

1024
00:32:41,819 --> 00:32:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] misli samo na svoje životinsko.

1025
00:32:43,319 --> 00:32:44,319
[SPEAKER_00] deti me ne skini iz križa,

1026
00:32:44,319 --> 00:32:45,140
[SPEAKER_00] da da je nešto pojedem

1027
00:32:45,140 --> 00:32:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] i popijem i točka.

1028
00:32:46,319 --> 00:32:48,400
[SPEAKER_00] Bi je na razini

1029
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] psihofizičkoj,

1030
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] a to je životinska razlina.

1031
00:32:51,579 --> 00:32:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] I životinje imaju

1032
00:32:52,319 --> 00:32:53,400
[SPEAKER_00] psihofizičku razlina

1033
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] i zato ni mogu

1034
00:32:54,059 --> 00:32:56,359
[SPEAKER_00] prepoznati Isusa kao Boga.

1035
00:32:56,359 --> 00:33:01,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, probajte.

1036
00:33:01,700 --> 00:33:02,819
[SPEAKER_00] Odlučite se za dobro.

1037
00:33:02,819 --> 00:33:04,339
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite kako dobijate nove oči.

1038
00:33:05,339 --> 00:33:07,339
[SPEAKER_00] i kako se i vaše zdravlje

1039
